WEBVTT

00:00:31.438 --> 00:00:37.056
Don't you notice yet?

00:00:37.056 --> 00:00:47.189
I'm starting to walk in ways I believe in. Here, again.

00:00:47.189 --> 00:00:49.517
Right.

00:00:49.517 --> 00:00:53.546
I knew it.

00:00:53.546 --> 00:00:57.250
I'm the same as ever.

00:00:57.250 --> 00:01:01.265
Maybe I'll try to start walking?

00:01:01.265 --> 00:01:04.247
In that distant time,

00:01:04.247 --> 00:01:11.691
I'm looking for meaning in life.

00:01:11.691 --> 00:01:19.231
The sound is bounding rhythmically.

00:01:19.231 --> 00:01:23.250
If we could put into words

00:01:23.250 --> 00:01:27.280
every second someone lives on,

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:31.278
we feel ourselves live on,

00:01:31.278 --> 00:01:35.293
like scattering words about.

00:01:35.293 --> 00:01:39.280
If we could put into words

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:43.324
every second someone lives on,

00:01:43.324 --> 00:01:47.340
we feel ourselves live on,

00:01:47.340 --> 00:01:51.224
like scattering words about.

00:01:51.224 --> 00:01:52.893
Here.

00:02:07.375 --> 00:02:12.936
Now, what you were seeing is

00:02:12.936 --> 00:02:21.208
your own self facing yourself on that day.

00:02:21.208 --> 00:02:23.129
Here, again

00:02:23.129 --> 00:02:29.385
...Sort of. So much happened, but

00:02:29.385 --> 00:02:33.117
I kept on living.

00:02:33.117 --> 00:02:40.122
I'll go again being still the same as that day.

00:02:40.122 --> 00:02:47.591
I'm looking for meaning in life

00:02:47.591 --> 00:02:55.121
...I walk because I was born.

00:02:55.121 --> 00:02:59.129
If we could put into words

00:02:59.129 --> 00:03:03.161
every second someone lives on,

00:03:03.161 --> 00:03:07.182
we feel ourselves live on,

00:03:07.182 --> 00:03:11.148
like scattering words about.

00:03:11.148 --> 00:03:15.150
If we could put into words

00:03:15.150 --> 00:03:19.172
every second someone lives on,

00:03:19.172 --> 00:03:23.179
we feel ourselves live on.

00:03:23.179 --> 00:03:27.141
like scattering words about.

00:03:27.141 --> 00:03:31.754
Here.

00:03:42.988 --> 00:03:46.990
If I can put into words

00:03:46.990 --> 00:03:51.008
every second I've lived,

00:03:51.008 --> 00:03:55.009
I should be able to start walking again.

00:03:55.009 --> 00:04:00.373
...Like you did one day.
